{{单双书号转换|'''爭愛'''}}（{{lang-en|"Love After War"}}），是[[羅賓·西克|羅賓·西克]]第5張專輯《{{le|爭愛|Love After War}}》的同名主打歌，於2011年10月11日發行。
歌曲獲得《告示牌》{{le|成人節奏藍調榜|Adult R&B Songs}}冠軍，並在年終榜上取得第5名的好成績。

== 製作 ==
{{单双书号转换|爭愛}}以[[升A小調|升A小調]]創作，每分鐘104拍，時長3分16秒<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://musicstax.com/track/love-after-war/0UBksVUOhS6GbXnlp4HHoS |title=Key and BPM of Love After War by Robin Thicke |website=musicstax.com |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-13 |archivedate=2020-11-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113034422/https://musicstax.com/track/love-after-war/0UBksVUOhS6GbXnlp4HHoS |deadurl=no}}</ref>，是一首有著[[当代节奏布鲁斯|当代节奏布鲁斯]]與{{le|白人靈魂樂|blue-eyed soul}}的[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行樂]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/06/arts/music/from-amy-winehouses-archives-lioness-new-music.html |title=Chipper Remnants of a Life Turned Sour |last=Chinen |first=Nate |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2011-12-06 |accessdate=2020-11-13 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113034600/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/06/arts/music/from-amy-winehouses-archives-lioness-new-music.html |archivedate=2020-11-13}}</ref>。歌曲的[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]由{{le|海普·威廉斯|Hype Williams}}執導，於2011年11月21日首映<ref name="rapup">{{cite web|url=https://www.rap-up.com/2011/11/21/video-robin-thicke-love-after-war/ |title= Video: Robin Thicke – ‘Love After War’ |publisher=Rap-Up.com |date=2011-11-21 |accessdate=2017-08-09 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809212448/https://www.rap-up.com/2011/11/21/video-robin-thicke-love-after-war/ |archivedate=2017-08-09}}</ref>。

